Key Match Events: India pulled off a shocking 119-113 win over Pakistan.
At one point, India had less than a 2% statistical chance of winning.
Fans were ecstatic as India managed to secure the win towards the end.
Post-Match Reflections: Fans expressed their excitement and surprise at India's unexpected victory.
Hem Nerkar commented on the amazing energy and unexpected win by India.
Bobby Mehra and Arjun Singh were thrilled to watch a cricket match close to home despite leaving early to avoid traffic.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Thousands of cricket fans descended on Long Island to watch the match.
There was reportedly a 90-10 split between India and Pakistan fans.
Fans from various locations, including the UK and different parts of the US, attended the match.
The match was part of the 2024 ICC Men’s T20 tournament.
